Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO HIGHER EDUCATION

Title: Relates to requiring a licensed massage therapist to present a state issued photo identification card when requested
Summary: Requires a licensed massage therapist to present a state issued photo identification card when requested at the time of performing services.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to requiring a licensed massage therapist to present a state issued photo identification card when requested at the time of performing services
